본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 substance use disorder (SUD / addiction medicine) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 약물 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_psychiatric` — psychiatric 은 mood / anxiety / psychosis / SERT 중심. SUD 는 reward-circuit (μ-OR / nAChR / GABA / DA) 중심 + harm reduction + relapse prevention 임상 framework. cross-link 은 comorbidity overlap 60-80%.)

scope:
- opioid use disorder (OUD — μ-opioid receptor)
- alcohol use disorder (AUD — cross-link `.roadmap.disease_hepatology`)
- nicotine use disorder (smoking cessation)
- stimulant use disorder (cocaine / methamphetamine — no FDA-approved pharmacotherapy)
- cannabis use disorder
- benzodiazepine use disorder (cross-link `.roadmap.disease_psychiatric`)
- opioid overdose reversal (naloxone / nalmefene)
- post-acute withdrawal syndrome (PAWS)
- harm reduction pharmacology
- contingency-management adjuvant pharmacology
- polysubstance use (fentanyl + xylazine "tranq")

