## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **stimulant use disorder = no FDA-approved pharmacotherapy** (2026-05-08 기준). cocaine + meth 의 medication gap 이 quantum-VQE 의 highest-leverage candidate space (TAAR1 / DRD3-selective / κ-OR antagonist).
2. **xylazine ("tranq") fentanyl polysubstance crisis** — 2023+ DEA-flagged. xylazine 가 α2-AR agonist 이지만 FDA-approved human reversal 없음. atipamezole human-trial 없음. quantum-VQE 의 α2-AR-A/B/C subtype selectivity 가 의의.
3. **naloxone OTC 2023** + **nalmefene Opvee 2023** = fentanyl-era overdose rescue revolution. 차이점: naloxone short-action (~30 min) → re-OD risk; nalmefene long-action (~8 h). quantum-VQE 의 binding-residence-time prediction 가 hxq-sud-mor-002 candidate motivation.
4. **GLP-1 AUD reduction signal 2024** = semaglutide reduces alcohol craving in observational + small RCT. dopamine reward-circuit modulation hypothesis. cross-metabolic 가 의외 의 SUD pathway.
5. **MOUD treatment gap**: only ~20% OUD patients receive MOUD (US). pharmacology gap 보다 access + stigma. quantum-VQE scope 한정.
6. **fentanyl vaccines NIDA Phase 1/2** = active-immunization 가 quantum scope 외부 (immunogen design 은 WEAVE/VIROCAPSID axis).
7. **ibogaine + psilocybin 5-HT2A multi-target** — quantum-VQE 의 multi-receptor selectivity 가 의미. 단 schedule I + cardiac risk = 임상 한정.
8. **OPRM1 A118G + CYP2D6 PM** = pharmacogenomic responder stratification. RIBOZYME / WEAVE personalized dosing axis 가 의미.
9. **disulfiram 1951** = 75-year-old AUD pharmacotherapy. modern QM-based ALDH selectivity refinement 가 hxq-sud-aldh-001 candidate motivation.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, SUD 임상 의미 한정.

